title: Help, Dr. Love! Someone's Stealing My Food...

description:
TUE 9/13 - Dr. Malachi Love-Robinson is BACK...in custody, that is. He gets today's hee-haw for frauding his way into a car dealership. But should he go to jail? You know who deserves to go to jail? Someone who steals food off of your plate. Even if it's 3 french fries. We'll discuss.
